# Homepage demo data

`src/data/homepage-demo-products.ts` is **homepage demo browse data only**.

- Do not use it as live retailer data or for production ranking.
- Demo prices, scores, offer counts, and discounts are seeded browse examples —
  always labeled as demo in the UI.
- Never wire demo ids into compare ranking, save/alerts persistence, cart lines,
  or checkout as if they were real catalog SKUs.
- Listing-backed Top Products / Best Deals cards must come from
  `getPopularComparisons` / `getBestDeals` (approved listings + PriceHistory).
- Demo tiles link to category/search browse — not fake product detail pages.
